blog.description: Hello, this is Palindrome! I'm currently doing my best to pretend that I'm a functional and well adjusted adult, with varying levels of success! Around this neck of the woods you'll find history stuff, nature stuff, whatever fandoms I'm into at the moment, fanfics I write when I can muster up the energy, the occasional mental breakdown and a variety of fun facts I come across or things I find interesting. Feel free to follow or drop me a line, I promise I'm quite tame.

summary: I’m really looking forward to Talks on Tuesday because I’m just dying for more information about our new favorite pastel hippie...
body: I’m really looking forward to Talks on Tuesday because I’m just dying for more information about our new favorite pastel hippie undertaker. I wanna know about his family and religion and just exactly how queer he is and in what way and if there’s actually something going on with why he’s so unhealthily thin and why his hair is pink (is it the lichen? does he dye it?) and just everything! I’m so excited to get to know our new boy!
